726784f-a.title: Queens: Grand Avenue - Calamus Road
726784f-a.text:
Grand Ave., north side, in proposed 82nd Street, between Calamus
Road and the New York Connecting Railroad, showing a shrouded view of a
John Gray house.built about 1656. The front of the structure was made
of small stones gathered on the farm.
Arthur White.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
